## Description {#details}

A critical data dependency descriptor.

<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/support/optimizedstructlayout-cpp/#a5208f2b0568d811c542f8d8097dbc035">Field</a> RegID is set to the invalid register for memory dependencies.
